1685602204:[TESTMD,0382]

Command list for MOBY 4000m
pext          : Get external pressure
pint          : Get internal vacuum
ui            : Get voltage/current
act           : Test actuators with pump deep and pump surface
fillb         : Surface pump until filling the bladder
bpopen        : Open bypass
bpclose       : Close bypass
date          : Get date
gps           : GPS synchronization
iridium       : Iridium transfer
mstart        : Start mermaid acq
mstop         : Stop mermaid acq
mdata         : Get mermaid datas
mchecksd      : Check mermaid sd card
mdump         : Send data REQUEST command with date and duration
scstart       : Start all scientifics board configured for stage[0]
scstop        : Stop all scientifics board configured for stage[0]
ls            : List files
cp            : Copy file or directory content on the desktop
rm            : Remove a file (rm all -> delete all files)
h             : Print command list
q             : Quit

Advanced
pumpdeep X    : Deep pump during Xs (low speed)
pumpsurface X : Surface pump during Xs (fast speed)
evh           : Open hydraulic electrovanne during 30s
bypass        : Open bypass during 30s
dvmine        : Devermine
nominal       : Nominal mode for consumption
cychydr       : Hydraulic cicuit test
mkdir         : Create folder
mv            : Move file
ps            : Process list

Set params
stage         : Stage settings
profil        : Profils parameters
buoy          : Buoy settings
p2t           : Pressure sensor settings
mermaid       : Mermaid cfg
upload        : On/Off Irid transfer


